metadata.name: Bullish
metadata.description:
Inspired by my trip for NFT NYC and meeting all those out there still building, I snapped this pic of the Wall Street Bull and transformed him into a Stoic Bull, modeled after my Bull (token #489) from The Stoics by Gabe Weis. 
Stay Stoic my friends as we await the next Bull Run. I did the good luck thing during my visit to the bull so it shouldn't be long now.
